The domain algorithms in this toolbox (LPC, IAIF, GCI/GOI detection,
weighted-LP glottal inverse filtering, LF-model fitting, voice source
feature extraction) are implemented from first principles, following the
published algorithm descriptions cited in each module's docstring. They are
not ported from existing source code.

Mike Brookes's VOICEBOX toolbox for MATLAB
(http://www.ee.ic.ac.uk/hp/staff/dmb/voicebox/voicebox.html) is gratefully
acknowledged as the reference implementation that many modules are checked
against during development.
